const configsKeys = Object.keys(configs);

export function generateRandomAvatarOptions() {
  const options = { }
  const keys = [...configsKeys]
  keys.forEach(key => {
    const configArray = configs[key];
    options[key] = configArray[Math.floor(Math.random()*configArray.length)];
  })

  return options;
}
